The '''Nagai expeditionary force''' was a massive collection of [[Cruiser/Legends|cruisers]] and [[Starship/Legends|starships]] that became home to the [[Nagai/Legends|Nagais]] after there homeworld of [[Nagi/Legends|Nagi]] was conquered by the [[Tof/Legends|Tofs]]. The fleet was first seen above [[Kinooine/Legends|Kinooine]] where they aligned themselves with the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] who aided the Nagai to avenge their defeat at Endor at the hands of the [[Alliance of Free Planets]]. The fleet later fought in the [[Second Battle of Endor]], the [[Battle of Iskalon (Nagai–Tof War)|Battle of Iskalon]], and other battles throughout the [[Nagai–Tof War]].

